<paragraph blockId="1.[151,782,593,620]" box="[151,782,593,620]" pageId="1" pageNumber="176">
<heading bold="true" box="[151,782,593,620]" fontSize="11" level="1" pageId="1" pageNumber="176" reason="1">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,782,593,620]" pageId="1" pageNumber="176">
Taxonomy of 
<taxonomicName authority="(Pictet 1836)" authorityName="Pictet" authorityYear="1836" baseAuthorityName="Pictet" baseAuthorityYear="1836" box="[321,782,593,620]" class="Insecta" family="Hydropsychidae" genus="Macrostemum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="176" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hyalinum">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[321,618,593,619]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="176">Macrostemum hyalinum</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Pictet, F. J." box="[633,774,594,620]" pageId="1" pageNumber="176" pagination="399 - 404" refId="ref5296" refString="Pictet, F. J. (1836) Description de quelques nouvelles especes de Nevropteres, du Musee de Geneve. Memoires de La Societe de Physique et d'Histoire Naturelle de Geneve, 7, 399 - 404." type="journal article" year="1836">Pictet 1836</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="1" pageNumber="176" type="reference_group">
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,664,977]" pageId="1" pageNumber="176">
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Pictet" baseAuthorityYear="1836" box="[151,423,664,688]" class="Insecta" family="Hydropsychidae" genus="Macrostemum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="176" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hyalinum">
<emphasis box="[151,423,664,688]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="176">Macrostemum hyalinum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is an important and unclear species of the genus for many reasons. It is one of the first 
<taxonomicName box="[151,281,700,725]" class="Insecta" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="176" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="order">Trichoptera</taxonomicName>
species described from the Neotropical region and, ironically, the taxonomic problems start in the original description. According to 
<bibRefCitation author="Pictet, F. J." box="[536,683,736,761]" pageId="1" pageNumber="176" pagination="399 - 404" refId="ref5296" refString="Pictet, F. J. (1836) Description de quelques nouvelles especes de Nevropteres, du Musee de Geneve. Memoires de La Societe de Physique et d'Histoire Naturelle de Geneve, 7, 399 - 404." type="journal article" year="1836">Pictet (1836)</bibRefCitation>
, the 
<typeStatus box="[735,783,737,761]" pageId="1" pageNumber="176">type</typeStatus>
locality for this species is “Indes orientales” [East Indies], but other authors argued that the species is Brazilian (
<bibRefCitation author="Burmeister, H." box="[767,962,772,797]" pageId="1" pageNumber="176" refId="ref4082" refString="Burmeister, H. (1839) Handbuch der Entomologie, Zweiter Band, Zweite Ubtheilung. Theod. Chr. Friedr. Enslin, Berlin, Germany." type="book" year="1839">Burmeister 1839</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Ulmer, G." box="[975,1128,772,797]" pageId="1" pageNumber="176" pagination="1 - 119" refId="ref5369" refString="Ulmer, G. (1905 b) Zur Kenntniss aussereuropaischer Trichopteren. Stettiner Entomologische Zeitung, 66, 1 - 119." type="journal article" year="1905">Ulmer 1905b</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Ulmer, G." box="[1141,1200,773,797]" pageId="1" pageNumber="176" refId="ref5392" refString="Ulmer, G. (1907) Trichopteren, Monographie der Macronematinae. Collections Zoologiques du Baron Edm. de Selys Longchamps, FI (2). Hayez, Bruxelles, pp. 1 - 121, plates I-VI." type="book" year="1907">1907</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Ulmer, G." box="[1212,1272,773,797]" pageId="1" pageNumber="176" pagination="383 - 414" refId="ref5433" refString="Ulmer, G. (1913) Verzeichnis der sudamerikanischen Trichopteren, mit Bemerkungen uber einzelne Arten. Deutsche Entomologische Zeitschrift, 1913, 383 - 414." type="journal article" year="1913">1913</bibRefCitation>
). 
<materialsCitation ID-GBIF-Occurrence="2234219956" country="France" location="South American" pageId="1" pageNumber="176" specimenCount="1">
<bibRefCitation author="Franca, D. &amp; Paprocki, H. &amp; Calor, A. R." pageId="1" pageNumber="176" pagination="301 - 335" refId="ref4739" refString="Franca, D., Paprocki, H. &amp; Calor, A. R. (2013) The genus Macrostemum Kolenati 1859 (Trichoptera: Hydropsychidae) in the Neotropical Region: Description of two new species, taxonomic notes, distributional records and key to males. Zootaxa, 3716, 301 - 335." type="journal article" year="2013">
<collectingCountry box="[1293,1369,773,796]" name="France" pageId="1" pageNumber="176">França</collectingCountry>
<emphasis box="[1378,1429,773,797]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="176">et al</emphasis>
. (2013)
</bibRefCitation>
listed the distribution of 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Pictet" baseAuthorityYear="1836" box="[508,649,808,832]" class="Insecta" family="Hydropsychidae" genus="Macrostemum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="176" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hyalinum">
<emphasis box="[508,649,808,832]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="176">M. hyalinum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03E187AADA79FFB42D85FDDDFBA105B0:8E976067DA79FFB42FBDFCA7FC880520" box="[687,873,808,833]" country="France" name="South American" pageId="1" pageNumber="176">South American</location>
</materialsCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,664,977]" pageId="1" pageNumber="176">
<bibRefCitation author="Kolenati, F. A." box="[199,377,844,869]" pageId="1" pageNumber="176" pagination="141 - 296" refId="ref4941" refString="Kolenati, F. A. (1859) Genera et Species Trichopterorum, Pars, Altera. Nouveaux Memoires de la Societe Imperialedes Naturalistes de Moscou, 11, 141 - 296." type="journal article" year="1859">Kolenati (1859)</bibRefCitation>
examined 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Pictet" baseAuthorityYear="1836" box="[499,640,845,869]" class="Insecta" family="Hydropsychidae" genus="Macrostemum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="176" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hyalinum">
<emphasis box="[499,640,845,869]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="176">M. hyalinum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in order to establish the genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Kolenati" authorityYear="1859" box="[988,1147,845,868]" class="Insecta" family="Hydropsychidae" genus="Macrostemum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="176" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[988,1147,845,868]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="176">Macrostemum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. The genus was proposed based on the mistaken observation of the absence of a pair of small apical spurs on each foretibia. The genus was established without a 
<typeStatus box="[394,442,917,941]" pageId="1" pageNumber="176">type</typeStatus>
species designation (
<bibRefCitation author="Kolenati, F. A." box="[680,845,916,941]" pageId="1" pageNumber="176" pagination="141 - 296" refId="ref4941" refString="Kolenati, F. A. (1859) Genera et Species Trichopterorum, Pars, Altera. Nouveaux Memoires de la Societe Imperialedes Naturalistes de Moscou, 11, 141 - 296." type="journal article" year="1859">Kolenati 1859</bibRefCitation>
). In 1957, Ulmer designated 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Pictet" baseAuthorityYear="1836" box="[1168,1309,917,941]" class="Insecta" family="Hydropsychidae" genus="Macrostemum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Trichoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="176" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hyalinum">
<emphasis box="[1168,1309,917,941]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="176">M. hyalinum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as the 
<typeStatus box="[1388,1436,917,941]" pageId="1" pageNumber="176">type</typeStatus>
species of the genus and 
<bibRefCitation author="Hollier, J. H." box="[430,591,952,977]" pageId="1" pageNumber="176" pagination="51 - 54" refId="ref4797" refString="Hollier, J. H. (2007) Continuite entre le Musee Academique et la Museum actuel l'exemple des &lt;&lt; Nevropteres du musee &gt;&gt; de F. - J. Pictet. Bulletin Romand D'Entomologie, 24, 51 - 54." type="journal article" year="2007">Hollier (2007)</bibRefCitation>
confirmed that the 
<typeStatus box="[810,858,953,977]" pageId="1" pageNumber="176">type</typeStatus>
series has been lost.
</paragraph>
